CREATE TABLE `t_user` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_name` varchar(100) NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '用户名',
  `mobile` char(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '手机号',
  `email` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '邮箱',
  `password` char(32) NOT NULL COMMENT '密码',
  `token` char(64) NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '会话token',
  `status` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '1' COMMENT 'Admin UserConst',
  `created_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `deleted_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `created_ip` char(15) NOT NULL COMMENT '注册ip',
  `last_login_ip` char(15) NOT NULL COMMENT '最后登录ip',
  `last_login_time` datetime NOT NULL COMMENT '最后登录时间',
  `remember_token` char(64) NOT NULL,
  `socialite_type` tinyint(3) DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '注册来源网站',
  `guarded` tinyint(1) unsigned DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '白名单 0无 1白名单',
  `source_sys` tinyint(1) unsigned DEFAULT '1' COMMENT '系统 1:www 2:020 3:400 4:Cloud',
  `source_way` tinyint(1) unsigned DEFAULT '1' COMMENT '来源 1:PC 2:weixin 3:H5 4:IOS 5:Android',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `user_name` (`user_name`),
  UNIQUE KEY `mobile` (`mobile`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=237 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COMMENT='用户表'
